Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.40,0:00:04.25,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{All right, thank you for taking care of it.}Vậy nhờ cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.25,0:00:05.88,Main,Mob Coworker 30s; female,0,0,0,,{One more thing, Katase-san.}À, Katase.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:08.61,Main,Mob Coworker 30s; female,0,0,0,,{Here's a little something...}Nếu được thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:11.77,Main,Mob Coworker 30s; female,0,0,0,,{It's for everyone in Product Development.}Hãy chia cho mọi người trong phòng nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:15.21,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Thank you so much!}Cảm ơn rất nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:20.07,Main,Shiori off script AD,0,0,0,,{Cookies, cookies...}Bánh quy bánh quy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:24.49,Main,Shiori off script AD,0,0,0,,{Sweet and yummy...}Ngọt và ngon...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:32.97,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I am exhausted.}Mệt quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:38.14,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{So much to do and learn \Nwhen you're new...}Quá nhiều việc phải ghi nhớ và làm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:40.03,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san.}Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:41.39,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,S-Senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:43.40,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Taking a break?}Giải lao à?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:44.64,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes.}V-Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:48.25,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Should I have told her first?}Tự bỏ đi giải lao...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:51.40,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-Sorry, I'll get right back to work—}X-Xin lỗi, em quay lại ngay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:55.86,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:57.78,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai?}Chị?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:03.37,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san.}Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:05.37,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes?}V-Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.53,0:01:09.75,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Which do you prefer: bears or bunnies?}Em thích gấu hay thỏ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:15.63,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Which is it? Bears or bunnies?}Cái nào hả? Gấu hay thỏ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:19.20,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Bears or bunnies...?}Gấu hay thỏ...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:21.16,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Right. Which is it?}Phải, cái nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.84,0:01:24.65,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I-If I had to choose, bears, I think...}N-Nếu phải chọn thì gấu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:25.77,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Understood.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:27.35,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Here!}Đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:29.40,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What is this?}Đây là?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:32.47,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{A little pick-me-up.}Cung cấp dinh dưỡng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.47,0:01:36.42,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{People tend to get peckish \Nand run-down around this time.}Mọi người hay đói bụng và mệt mỏi vào giờ này mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.42,0:01:40.16,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Someone from general affairs gave these to me,}Người bên phòng tổng vụ cho đó,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:43.66,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{and I'm going to share them \Nwith everyone else later on...}và chị định chia cho mọi người sau...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:47.11,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{But you get yours early, Shinozaki-san!}Nhưng em sẽ được ưu tiên lấy sớm, Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.03,0:01:51.92,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Just don't tell anyone, okay?}Đừng nói ai đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:58.10,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{There's a senpai where I work... \Nwho is tiny and cute.}Đàn chị chỗ làm... nhỏ bé và dễ thương.
