Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:34.17,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Good morning.}Chào buổi sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.74,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I guess I'm first in, today.}Hôm nay đếm sớm nhất à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.06,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Aw...}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:50.37,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Good morning.}Chào buổi sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:57.43,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai never leaves her stuff \Non her desk like that.}Chị ấy chưa từng bỏ túi lên bàn bao giờ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.82,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{G-Good morning...}C-Chào buổi sáng...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.36,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-S-Senpai?!}C-C-Chị?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:05.26,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.28,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What are you doing?!}Chị làm gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:09.53,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I... just...}Chị... chỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:11.27,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{dropped this pen...}làm rơi bút...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:13.29,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Let me get out of your way!}Em sẽ tránh ra ngay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:15.40,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'd appreciate that.}C-Cảm ơn nhé...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:17.40,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpa...}Chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:29.79,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai's breasts!}Ngực của chị ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.72,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Sorry! I'm so sorry! Let me move right now!}E-Em xin lỗi! Để em tránh ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:35.29,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You don't have to panic! It's okay!}Em không cần phải hoảng đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:43.17,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{What a lovely morning you two are having.}Lại một buổi sáng quấn quýt nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:47.12,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I-It's not what you think! \NIt's just a coincidence!}K-Không phải đâu! Chỉ là trùng hợp thôi ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:50.18,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You, too, Hayakawa?!}Cả cậu nữa hả Hayakawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:53.06,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I think that dirty thoughts are bad.}Suy nghĩ dâm dục là xấu xa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:57.74,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Seriously, it's just a coincidence!}Chỉ là trùng hợp thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:05.50,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai, were the documents I submitted okay?}Tài liệu em gửi ổn không ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:09.58,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Give me a second and I can check.}Chờ chị kiểm tra lại nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:14.83,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What the—?!}Cái này--?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:17.62,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Did I mess up?}Em làm sai gì ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:19.90,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{These documents...}Tài liệu này...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:25.13,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You did a really good job!}Em làm tốt lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:27.87,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Good boy!}Ngoan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:30.76,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{U-Um, Senpai...?}C-Chị ơi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.27,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Very, very good.}Ngoan lắm ngoan lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.30,Main - Top,Shiinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai...}Chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:36.99,Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,{My subordinates at work get along very well.}Cấp dưới của mình khá thân thiết.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:37.21,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You worked hard, huh?}Em đã cố hết sức nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:38.27,Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,{Honestly...}Thực lòng...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.47,Main - Top,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's not that big a deal...}Cũng không có gì đâu ạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:43.00,Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,{Would an ordinary pair of \Ncoworkers get along like that?}Một cặp đồng nghiệp bình thường là phải thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:43.78,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I never want to miss \Na chance to offer praise!}Chị sẽ luôn khen em khi làm tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:44.78,Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,{It feels a little more significant than that.}Mình không nghĩ vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:47.37,Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,{More than coworkers, it's like they're...}Hơn cả đồng nghiệp, cứ như hai đứa nó...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:54.66,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Scouting a location for a drinking party?}Kiểm tra nơi tổ chức tiệc?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:59.92,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Right. I was supposed to go, \Nbut something came up kind of abruptly.}Ừm, tôi định đi nhưng có việc đột xuất.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:02.36,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Sure, I can do that.}Vâng, em sẽ làm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:04.67,Main,Akiba,0,0,0,,{What a relief. Please do.}May quá. Cảm ơn cậu nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:09.80,Main,Akiba,0,0,0,,{And since the more opinions, the better, \Nwhy don't you join him, Katase-san?}Vì cần nghe nhiều ý kiến nên em đi cùng nhé, Katase?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.74,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yay, I'd love to!}Vâng, em đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:18.30,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I wonder what kind of place it is.}Không biết quán đó thế nào nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:20.69,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I hope the food is tasty!}Hi vọng đồ ăn ngon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:25.13,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's supposed to be \Nthe top floor of this building.}Có vẻ ở trên tầng cao nhất của toà nhà này.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:26.91,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{This should be fun!}Đáng mong chờ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:31.05,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Since our manager chose it, \NI bet it's pretty fancy.}Vì quản lý đã chọn nên em nghĩ sẽ tuyệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:35.70,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I know what you mean, \Nthe night view is bound to be pretty.}Phải nhỉ, khung cảnh chắc đẹp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:35.70,Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,{Good, smooth sailing so far...}Ngon, rất suôn sẻ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:38.96,Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,{Now they just need to keep it up, \Nafter going into the restaurant.}Giờ cứ tiếp tục vào nhà hàng và sau đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:43.46,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I think I might be a little drunk...}Chị nghĩ mình hơi say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.55,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-Senpai...}C-Chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:50.54,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'm not letting you go home tonight.}Em sẽ không để chị về đêm nay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.56,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I wouldn't want to.}Chị không về đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:59.37,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san, I...}Chị Shinozaki, em...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:01.75,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai... I...}Em...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:10.00,Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,{That was a close one. \NI almost let my own fantasy fry my brain.}Nguy quá, tí nữa thì bị mộng tưởng nuốt chửng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:10.94,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Manager?}Quản lý?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:12.94,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa-san?!}Hayakawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:17.29,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I thought you said you had \Nsudden business to attend to?}Em tưởng anh bảo có việc bận?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:24.76,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Oh, I get it.}À, em hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:26.84,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{You're curious, too, aren't you, Hayakawa-san?}Em cũng tò mò phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.51,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{He's your childhood friend, and coworker...}Bạn thuở nhỏ và đồng nghiệp của mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:30.51,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Wait, no!}Khoan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:34.51,Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,{How could I be so cruel?!}Sao mình có thể nhẫn tâm đến thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:38.72,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{If you need anything, you know who to ask.}Nếu cần gì chứ hỏi nhé?
