Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:50.11,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad250,0\p1\pos535,119\an5\bord0\shad0}m 0 0 l 118 0 l 118 168 l 0 168
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.44,0:07:50.11,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad250,0\pos536.5,119\fnComic Sans MS\an5\b1\fs24\c&H000000&\bord0\shad0}{Or the\Nreunited\Nchildhood\Nfriends/\Nclassmates\Nromance.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:50.11,Narration,Akina,0,0,0,,{Or the reunited childhood \Nfriends/classmates romance.}Hay màn đoàn tụ giữa bạn thuở nhỏ/ bạn học cùng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:53.15,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Which should I be rooting for?!}Mình phải cổ vũ cho cặp nào đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:57.03,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Why am I even included?! \NI don't need that kind of support!}Mắc gì lại cả em nữa? Em ủng hộ bọn họ!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.97,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{What, really?}Thật á?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:02.68,Main,Haykawa,0,0,0,,{Seriously, Shinozaki and I just go way back!}Vâng, em với Shinozaki chỉ là mối quan hệ bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:03.63,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Seriously?}Thật hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:04.54,Main,Haykawa,0,0,0,,{Seriously.}Thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.18,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I see...}Vậy à...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:09.05,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Why do you seem disappointed?}Sao anh có vẻ thất vọng thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.87,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Well, be that as it may,}Nói tóm lại,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:15.20,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{since you're here anyway, \Nyou should join me. Let's go!}em đã ở đây rồi thì tham gia với tôi không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.55,Main - Top,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Wha...}Cái...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:19.91,Main,Server female; 20s,0,0,0,,{You have reservations, correct? \NWe're pleased to have you.}Quý khách đã đặt bàn ạ? Xin mời.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:21.72,Main,Server female; 20s,0,0,0,,{Right this way.}Lối này.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:25.09,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Sneak, sneak, sneak...}Lén lút, lén lút...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:26.90,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{How did I get roped into this?}Sao mình lại bị kéo theo chứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:32.16,Main,Server,0,0,0,,{Please, have a seat.}Xin mời ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:35.82,Main,Server,0,0,0,,{These are our special tables \Nthat let you enjoy the night view.}Đây là bạn đặc biệt có thể ngắm cảnh đêm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:39.83,Main,Server,0,0,0,,{I'll be back for your order in a bit.}Tôi sẽ quay lại sau khi quý khách gọi món.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:44.58,Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,{How's that? Getting dropped into those \Ncouples seats must be pretty exciting, right?}Sao nào? Ghế ngồi đôi tuyệt vời lắm nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:48.09,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{This should bring \Nthe two of them closer together, and...}Thế này thì khoảng cách giữ họ sẽ gần lại và...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:51.40,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Not a lot of restaurants \Nwith side-by-side seating.}Không nhiều nhà hàng có ghế đôi thế này đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:52.59,Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,{He didn't catch on!}Không nhận ra à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:55.48,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{This menu is huge, I don't know where to start.}Thực đơn nhiều quá làm chị phân vân ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:08:56.84,Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,{She's focused on food!}Còn bên này lo ăn không thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:59.39,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I've never eaten somewhere like this before.}Em lần đầu ăn ở nhà hàng như này đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.18,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Neither have I.}Chị cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:04.41,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's what I'd expect from our manager, \Nthough. He's really got style.}Đúng là quản lý có khác, có mắt ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:08.23,Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,{They're not getting what I was going for, \Nbut they seem happy, so I guess it's okay?!}Mấy đứa nó có vẻ vui nên là... được nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:10.91,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{You're really enjoying this, Manager.}Anh thích chuyện này quá nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:12.48,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{You bet I am!}Chứ gì nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.48,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{You see...}Anh ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:18.12,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{The thing is...}Anh ấy nhé...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:24.87,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Nothing makes me happier than \Ncheering on someone else's love life.}Không gì làm anh vui bằng việc\N hỗ trợ tình cảm cho người khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:30.75,Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I think our boss might be a weirdo.}Có vẻ cấp trên công ty mình hơi kì lạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:32.80,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{This is rough, though...}Nhưng mà phiền ghê...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.47,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I thought the couples seating \Nwould get their pulses pounding.}Anh nghĩ chọn ghế cặp đôi sẽ khiến họ hồi hộp cơ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.73,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, check it out, Senpai. Over there!}A, nhìn kìa chị! Bên kia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:40.51,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What is it?}Đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:43.93,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{That's our office right there, isn't it?}Kia là văn phòng chúng ta nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.77,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Where?! I want to see!}Đâu? Chị muốn thấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:04.90,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I knew it! It's easier to see from up here!}Quả nhiên nhìn từ đây dễ thấy hơn nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:09.08,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-Senpai... s-so close...}C-Chị ơi... Gần quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:10.54,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{a-and her....}v-và...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:13.55,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{b-b-boobs are...!}n-ngực...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:17.05,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Is everything okay?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:19.61,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yes, it's a nice view...}Vâng, đẹp lắm ạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.93,Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,{Smooth move, Katase-san!}Katase, đỉnh lắm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:25.61,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Are you okay, Shinozaki-san? \NYour face is red.}Em ổn chứ Shinozaki? Mặt đỏ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.84,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Yes, that's the spirit!}Phải thế chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:30.19,Main - Top,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Uh, yes, it's just, \Nkinda hot in here, y'know?}À vâng, trong đây hơi nóng...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:29.50,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Now, Shinozaki-kun just needs to \Ndo something to thrill Katase-san...}Giờ thì Shinozaki chỉ cần 'Nlàm gì đó khiến Katase lạc nhịp...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:34.19,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{That's it... just a little more...}Thêm... chút nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.32,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That was a big meal.}No quá đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:42.45,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah! And it all was great.}Vâng! Rất tuyệt vời ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:48.14,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Well, we've got work tomorrow. \NMaybe we should wrap it up for tonight.}Mai còn có việc nên hôm nay kết thúc thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:50.71,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, man, it's that late already?}Trễ thế rồi ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:55.70,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I was hoping we could stay \Na bit longer. That's a shame.}Em hi vọng được ở bên chị thêm chút nữa, tiếc ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:11:00.54,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You wanted to stay together... longer?}Em muốn... ở thêm chút nữa hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:05.74,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Does that mean...?}Tức là...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:08.49,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Let me walk you to the station.}Em sẽ tiễn chị ra ga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:12.17,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, right! Thank you.}V-Vâng! Cảm ơn em.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:13.63,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Everything okay?}Mọi chuyện ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:14.98,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I-It's fine!}O-Ổn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:19.40,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What was I thinking...?}Mình vừa nghĩ gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.96,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Um, Senpai?}Chị?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:26.26,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Uh, well.. it's... um...}À thì... là...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:30.96,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I knew you had it in you, Shinozaki-kun!}Cậu có thể làm được nếu muốn mà, Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:35.05,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Whoa, Manager!\NPlease don't turn to sugar grains on me!}Khoan đã! Anh đang biến thành đường kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:39.87,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Thank you for walking me to the station!}Cảm ơn vì đưa chị ra ga nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:42.01,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{See you tomorrow, Senpai!}Gặp chị sau!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:46.55,Main - Top,Eyecatch Sign/Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{My Tiny Senpai}{\i0}{.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.14,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Morning, Shinozaki.}Chào buổi sáng Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:57.83,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Hey, good morning.}Chào.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.28,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{An umbrella?}Dù?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:03.53,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{The weather didn't mention rain, did it?}Hôm nay có mưa đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:05.40,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, this...}À đây là...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.29,Flashback_Italics - Top,TV,0,0,0,,{Your lucky item today is an umbrella!}Hôm nay vật may mắn của bạn là dù.
