Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:11.29,Flashback_Italics - Top,TV,0,0,0,,{Carry one, and unexpected fortune \Nmay find you.}Hãy mang theo nó và vận may bất ngờ sẽ đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:13.19,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{So it said.}Nó nói thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:14.36,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:30.52,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Thank goodness I brought an umbrella...}May mà mang theo dù...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:41.32,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai... Did she not bring an umbrella?}Chị ấy không mang dù à?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:43.72,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Excuse me!}À vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:48.25,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Would you like to share mine?}Chị đi cùng em nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:53.82,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yes!}Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:04.16,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Sharing an umbrella with Senpai...}Đi chung dù với chị ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:06.18,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Man, this really is lucky!}Quá may mắn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:13.21,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{B-But... I'm so nervous, \NI've barely said anything...}N-Nhưng mình lo quá nên chẳng nói được gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:19.32,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Your shoulder is getting wet, Shinozaki-san.}Em bị ướt vai kìa Shinozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:22.98,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, I'm sorry if I worried you!}A, em quên mất...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:27.49,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{W-Well...}C-Chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:30.14,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{h-how did you end up as my senpai, anyway?}tại sao chị lại là đàn chị của em?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:31.72,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{By working at our company first.}Thì vào công ty trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:33.00,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{That makes sense!}Phải nhỉ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:35.45,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What kind of animals do you like, Senpai?!}Chị thích động vật gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:36.62,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Cats!}Mèo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:37.75,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I knew that!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:41.28,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{This is awful! I suck at talking!}Tệ quá! Mình tệ khoản nói chuyện ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:45.52,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san! You don't have to \Nforce yourself to talk.}Shinozaki, em không cần ép mình quá đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:48.73,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm enjoying walking home together as it is.}Chị thích đi về chung với em mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.55,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{R-Right...}V-Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:58.52,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it, you always speak up \Nwhen a meeting gets quiet, don't you?}Nghĩ lại thì, em lúc nào cũng nói gì đó\Nmỗi khi cuộc họp trở nên yên ắng nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:02.25,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I start to panic \Nwhen no one is talking...}Vâng, em trở nên lo lắng khi không ai nói gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:05.28,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's even more nerve-wracking \Nwith the section chief in attendance.}Có trưởng bộ phận nên còn căng thẳng hơn nhỉ?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:05.99,0:14:10.96,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{He looks so scary... \NI know he's actually nice, though.}Anh ấy tuy hơi đáng sợ... nhưng là người tốt.
