Dialogue: 2,0:14:10.96,0:14:13.29,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I know exactly what you mean!}Chị hiểu mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.72,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I wish I knew how to \Nget over being so nervous.}Em muốn chữa cái tính lo âu này quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:19.13,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'd hate for it to cause trouble.}Em ghét phải gây rắc rối...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:21.92,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You don't need to be so tense about it.}Không cần phải gấp gáp đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:25.32,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Everybody learns how these \Nthings work as time goes on.}Làm gì có ai làm tốt ngay từ đầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:29.08,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Besides, the chief has mentioned \Nhow the way you ask a lot of questions}Với cả nhờ em nói nhiều như thế
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:33.12,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{makes it easier for everyone else to speak up.}nên không khí trở nên dễ thở hơn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:36.49,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Th-That's great to hear.}E-Em rất cảm ơn ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:43.15,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, sorry, I wanted to stop by the book store \Nbefore heading home, so I'll be going now.}A, chị muốn ghé cửa hàng sách nên là đến đây thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:46.97,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{In that case, if you want, \Nyou can take my umbrella.}Vậy thì em sẽ đưa dù cho chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:54.73,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I had a great time talking!}Được nói chuyện với em vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:58.14,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Let's give it our all at work again, \Ntomorrow, Shinozaki-san.}Mai gặp lại nhé, Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:14:59.74,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{See you then!}Chào em!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:05.13,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{She had one all along?!}Có mang theo à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.43,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Ủa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:16.33,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Is Shinozaki-san taking the day off?}Shinozaki nghỉ bữa nay à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:19.68,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{He's sick, apparently. Called in this morning.}Có vẻ là bị cảm. Sáng nay em ấy có gọi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.25,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, I see...}Vậy ạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:25.45,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Your shoulder is getting wet, Shinozaki-kun.}Vai em ướt kìa, Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.57,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, I'm sorry!}À vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:30.92,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Want to check up on him?}Muốn kiểm tra thử hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:32.57,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Wh-Why would I do that?!}T-Tại sao em phải làm thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:35.08,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Well, he is your only kohai, after all!}Thì là đàn em của em mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:38.08,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{He's mentioned that living \Non his own is proving to be a handful.}Nghe nói em ấy sống một mình đó, vất vả ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.22,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Still not going down...}Chưa hạ sốt nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:59.93,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Well, it's my own fault for going \Ninto shock in the middle of the rain.}Thôi, cũng tại mình tự nhiên đứng tắm mưa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:07.22,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Coming...}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:12.36,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{How are you feeling, Shinozaki-san?}Em thế nào Shinozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.73,0:16:15.68,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai?! You went out of your way to visit me?!}C-Chị đến đây luôn ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:16.87,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, come now.}Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:19.77,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I was just in the neighborhood.}Chị có việc gần đây thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:22.46,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{And you've been out \Nfor three days, so I was worried,}Và em đã nghỉ 3 ngày nên chị hơi lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:25.72,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{and I heard living on your own \Nwas rough for you,}Nghe nói em sống một mình nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:26.88,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{so I brought some supplies.}Nên chị định ghé giúp đỡ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:29.88,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Thank you so much. That is really thoughtful...}Cảm ơn chị vì đã quan tâm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:40.50,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{How about I make something for you?}Để chị nấu gì cho nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:52.30,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What is even happening...?}Chuyện này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:55.34,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I feel crazy-happy.}Mình cảm thấy hạnh phúc quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:58.49,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{There you go.}Của em đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:16:59.69,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Thank you for the food.}Em ăn đây ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:01.60,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's good!}Ngon quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.41,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm glad you like it!}May mà em thích nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:06.67,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'll tidy up and do some laundry, too.}Chị sẽ dọn dẹp một chút nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:08.44,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Thanks again.}Cảm ơn chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:10.92,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, wait, my underwear!}Cơ mà quần lót!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:14.76,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I really appreciate you doing all this.}Em thực sự biết ơn chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.18,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, it's all right.}Không có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:20.49,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Despite appearances, \NI'm more the big sister type.}Trông thế thôi chứ chị\N là một người chị thứ thiệt đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:26.75,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I am so, incredibly, crazily happy right now,}Mình... hạnh phúc muốn chết...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:30.39,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I don't even want to get better anymore.}Không muốn khỏi bệnh nữa luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:38.95,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Well, sorry to intrude. Make sure to stay \Nwarm, and get some more rest, okay?}Xin lỗi vì đã làm phiền nhé.\N Nhớ giữ ấm và nghỉ ngơi đi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:41.64,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You're a real life-saver, Senpai.}Cảm ơn chị rất nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:44.81,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it, what were \Nin you in the neighborhood for?}Cơ mà chị có việc gần khu này ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.83,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{To see a movie with a friend.}Chị đi xem phim cùng bạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:51.21,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Huh? But the theater is in the opposite \Ndirection of my house from the train station...}Ủa? Em tưởng rạp chiếu phim ở hướng ngược lại?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:55.02,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{W-Well, uh,}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:57.80,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm running short on time, so...}chị phải đi đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:04.60,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I messed up...}Mình lại thế rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:09.10,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Maybe I got too excited,\Nbecause he's my only kohai.}Mình đã quá háo hức vì em ấy là đàn em duy nhất...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:14.92,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I guess I'll buy something microwaveable...}Mua tạm đồ hâm nóng rồi ăn vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:21.62,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs14\c&H1A1C1E&\bord0\shad0\pos(298.667,302.666)\frz27.05\fax.2\frx10\fry356}{Simple, Delicious\NRecipe Book!\N}{\fs8\c&H5189C4&}{What to make when someone's sick}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:28.92,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Maybe something to cook, too.}Thôi, mua gì có thể nấu được đi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:31.94,Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,{Mission accomplished!}Nhiệm vụ hoàn thành!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:37.50,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{A present for Senpai?}Quà cho chị ấy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:39.68,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Well, it's less a present and more...}Nói là quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.69,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{A token of my thanks?}Chỉ là quà cảm ơn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:43.18,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Thanks for what?}Vì điều gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:46.60,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{She came over and looked \Nafter me when I was sick.}Hôm bữa bị bệnh chị ấy có ghé qua.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.41,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{She even cooked for me.}Và nấu ăn cho tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.41,0:18:51.31,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Maybe I should get something \Nunobtrusive, like candy.}Quả nhiên là nên mua bánh trái gì đó nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:54.22,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Are you stupid?!}Cậu bị ngốc à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:57.87,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Why would you give someone who went to your \Nhouse and cooked for you when you were sick}Tại sao lại tặng cùng một món quà cho đối tác vào lễ obon
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:19:01.11,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,cho đàn chị đã đến nhà và \Nchăm sóc cậu những ngày bị bệnh hả?{the same gift you'd pass onto \Na business partner for the Bon holiday?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:04.12,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{A business Bon gift?!}Quà cho đối tác?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:06.65,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Well? Was the food good?}Thế có ngon không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:08.62,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah, very much so.}Ngon chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:11.53,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I-It was downright delicious....}C-Chị ấy nấu ngon lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:13.63,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{And I think she likes to cook.}Và tớ nghĩ chị ấy có vẻ thích nấu ăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:18.04,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Then get her an apron, and say \N"Please come and cook for me again!"}Vậy thì tặng tạp dề và nói "Lần tới\N hãy đến nấu cho em ăn nữa!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:20.01,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Where did that come from?!}Sao lại nói thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:23.69,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Isn't it considered rude to give \Nnon-consumables since they take up space?}Tặng quà là đồ dùng sẽ làm đối phương khó xử mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:26.91,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I say you need to give her something \Nthat will stick around and remind her of you.}Cậu nên tặng gì đó mà khiến chị ấy nhớ về mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:29.02,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Remind her of what, exactly?!}Nhớ về tớ á?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:34.02,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What should I do?}Sao giờ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:39.28,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I ended up actually buying one \Non impulse, but I think...}Mình đã mua nó trong lúc cao hứng nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:42.62,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{This might be a lot harder to \Ncasually hand to her!}Thế này thì sao dám tặng tận tay chứ?
