Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.28,0:19:43.03,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fnArial\b1\fs18\an5\bord1.5\pos(148,70)\fscy140}{Shinozaki's }{\fs14\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\bord2}{Gift Giving Ease\N}{\fs20}{Ranking!!}Những món quà dễ tặng
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.28,0:19:43.03,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(148,133.333)\an5\fs18\fscy120\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0}{1 Souvenirs Snacks\N2 Thank-you gifts Snacks\N3 Parting gifts Snacks}1 Đặc sản - Bánh kẹo\N 2 Quà cảm ơn - Bánh kẹo\\N 3 Quà tiễn biệt - Bánh kẹo\
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:46.03,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Maybe I should go with candy after all.}Quả nhiên là bánh kẹo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:48.07,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Good morning.}Chào buổi sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:51.16,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{G-G-Good morning, Senpai!}C-C-Chào chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:54.04,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What's wrong? You seem anxious.}Sao thế? Trông em có vẻ lo lắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:57.30,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Well, it's nothing, really...}Không có gì ạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:02.30,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Th-The gift! I need to give it to her!}Q-Quà! Mình phải đưa cho chị ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:05.67,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{But what if she thinks it's too much?}Nhưng nhỡ chị ấy nghĩ nhiều thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:10.28,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Then again, I don't think \NSenpai would feel that way...}Chị ấy sẽ không làm thế đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:12.71,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Excuse me!}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:18.40,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Thank you very much for the other day.}Cảm ơn chị vì chuyện lần trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.03,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I got this for you...}Nếu được thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:30.38,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Um... I'm sorry if you don't like it...}À... nếu chị không thích thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:32.12,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{An apron?}Tạp dề?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:35.67,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's too much, isn't it?!}Quả nhiên là phiền phức?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:41.45,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Thank you so much!}Cảm ơn em nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:45.80,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Thank goodness, she seems to like it...}May quá, có vẻ chị ấy thích nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.68,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{W-Well...}À vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:51.62,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'm sure you'll look nice in it,}Em chắc chị mặc vào sẽ đẹp lắm,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:54.69,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{so I hope you'll use it at home.}nên hi vọng hãy dùng nó ở nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:58.41,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You wouldn't mind me \Ncoming by your house again?}Chị đến nhà em nữa được hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:03.45,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I-I meant at your own house, not mine...}Y-Ý em là nhà chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:06.45,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, right! That makes sense. Sorry about that.}À phải nhỉ! Chị xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:11.29,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That was such a silly assumption to make...}Sao mình lại nói ra câu đáng xấu hổ đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:14.21,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Though, if you wouldn't mind, Senpai...}Nhưng nếu không phiền...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:18.21,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'd be really glad to have you over again.}Em sẽ rất vui khi chị ghé nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:25.18,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Well...  Someday might be nice.}Vậy ngày nào chị rảnh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:27.93,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Right, well... whenever is good for you.}Vâng... ngày nào cũng được...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:30.65,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{You two want the afternoon off?}Hai em có muốn nghỉ chiều nay không?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:33.02,Main,Both,0,0,0,,{Manager, give it a rest!}Tha cho bọn em đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.02,Main,,0,0,0,,
